    "description": "And when she drank the last of the poison vial, all she could think was... <br><strong>GOBBLEDYGUNK!</strong> <br>...also known as The God of Second Chances.<br><br>After committing suicide, our protagonist, Duo, finds that she misses the Land of the Living and wishes to return— A sentiment held by most residents of the Land of the Dead. Gobbledygunk seizes this opportunity to satisfy his twisted desires and pit all the residents of the Land of the Dead against each other in a fight to the death! <br><br>Upon death, you may choose to participate in this battle to gain entry back to the Land of the Living—with a wish granted to you by Gobbledygunk himself! The catch is, that every participant in his sick game is morphed into a form that reflects their deepest regrets from their old life. But what was meant to be a curse turned out to be a blessing for Duo, as she gained the ability to possess powerful Vessels and gain an advantage in the competition!<br><br>Now with the resources to claim her Second Chance, Duo climbs Fort Gobbledy hoping to finish what she started back in the Land of the Living...<br><br>This Game Features...<br>...3 PLAYABLE VESSELS with UNIQUE ABILITIES!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3245210/extras/c2b88cd31dd3ac00e3ed1ab17188b20c.avif?t=1728389996\" width=240 height=120 /></span><br><br>...VARIOUS FOES with TRICKY PATTERNS!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3245210/extras/5e79c59d5e352ce08a571c60acfb4f18.avif?t=1728389996\" width=240 height=120 /></span><br><br>...CHALLENGING CAMPAIGN and ENDLESS MODES!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3245210/extras/b3513e3a95c1ffc36c6453a799433fe9.avif?t=1728389996\" width=240 height=120 /></span><br><br>...a CAPTIVATING STORY for the ages! <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3245210/extras/f9c7f4f0771a14fbb8311aeb6bb2e70d.avif?t=1728389996\" width=240 height=120 /></span><br><br>...SECRETS and CUSTOMIZATION options!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3245210/extras/c17fb4f52f264927f8baa3130c32c1bf.avif?t=1728389996\" width=240 height=120 /></span><br><br>...3 JAMMING SOUNDTRACKS?!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3245210/extras/760434045c85a40e1c5017abb3c10942.avif?t=1728389996\" width=240 height=120 /></span><br><br><br>Reclaim your Second Chance in... <strong>VIRULENT VESSELS: THE LEGEND OF GOBBLEDYGUNK!</strong>",
